{
  "stem": "8610.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was deeply moved, the fact that they had been survivors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- many of them had been in Theresienstadt and had come back to Germany, in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to them, look, I'm only here for a day or so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you want to communicate with anybody anywhere in the world to tell them you're alive, I will collect your letters tomorrow morning.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I will distribute them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I collected them on the Sunday morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I got back to my office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I separated them according to countries-- to Palestine-- it was easy-- South Africa, to England.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a sort of a-- there was a unit that was responsible for tracing people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I sent them off in batches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I heard no more, until one bright day I was hauled up before my local chief chaplain, who said to me, you have been breaking the law.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now what have I done?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Apparently, somebody had received such a letter, wrote to a relative in Switzerland to say that they had heard so-and-so was still alive in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you want to communicate with them, send me the letter, and I will send it off.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was accused by military-- this was intercepted by military intelligence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they duly-- I was duly reprimanded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was breaking the laws of censorship and whatnot, acting as a sort of unofficial postman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I said to my chief, who was my superior in rank, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] do you mind if I speak to you as a clergyman to clergyman?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or must I speak to you as a major to a colonel?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, he said, of course, I'm a clergyman first.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
